
Project Task:
-------------------
1. Create a sample node-js application.
2. Containarized sample application using docker - Image created.
3. Created a bash script to setup LAMP stack and AWS cliin an AWS Instance, also included the script to create a container from the image previously created.
4. Created a bash script to generate a backup of the server and upload the backfile files to the AWS S3.
5. Created a cron-job to run the backup script each day a week.
6. Initiate GIT from the project folder and create an Gitlab remote repo for the project.
7. Create an AWS codepipeline also using Sonarcube for testing the code.
8. Setup observability using Promtheus and grafana.